ion", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBqah16L.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/AprilSpark1890/status/2075291406742979050", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Mamdumi's New York: Muslim couple chases a man out of a park for having a dog. Make sure this doesn't happen in YOUR state! There's no way the guy with the dog could take any sort of legal action in any sense, and that means that Islamic Sharia law is already in effect. ", "last_comment_created": 1783705613780, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 17, "score_up": 202, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 1557, "created": 1783623003000, "id": "2075291406742979050", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2075291303617716224/img/DPEwZgWJKDI0zcJW.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2075291303617716224/pl/SfpMXNIubH0pN1vu.m3u8?v=20a", "aspectRatio": [9, 16], "heightRatio": 177, "type": "video/mp4", "url": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2075291303617716224/vid/avc1/320x568/-mF4YYb6mh0Q5pps.mp4"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1953903876882530304/KI3AB4MC_normal.jpg", "displayName": "\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8 \ud835\udcd0\ud835\udcdf\ud835\udce1\ud835\udcd8\ud835\udcdb \ud835\udce2\ud835\udcdf\ud835\udcd0\ud835\udce1\ud835\udcda\ud835\udce2 \ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8", "username": "AprilSpark1890"}, "content": "Mamdumi\u2019s New York City\n       \ud83d\udc7f\ud83e\udd2c\ud83e\udd2c\ud83e\udd2c\ud83e\udd2c\ud83e\udd2c\ud83d\udc7f\nThis American is literally being chased out of his own park by Muslims.  I don\u2019t have the full story but you can hear them calling him a r@cist and are aggressively yelling at his dog.  We all know that they hate dogs.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 5654}}, "post_flair_text": "SAVE AMERICA", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBqbnTkG", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 78, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8722000, "raw_content": "Maybe an upper limit of 80 or so?\n\nSimple qualification rule:\n\nTerm for which a person is running must end no later than 180 days after that candidate's 80th birthday.\n\nAdmittedly, Chuck Grassley has remained healthy and lucent well into advance age, but that is not the norm.\n\nThurmond, Byrd, Feinstein, McConnell, etc prove there needs to be an age limit.\n\nHow many of you would board a commercial airliner w/ two 80-yr old pilots?\n\nHow many would have surgery performed by an 80-yr old surgeon?", "author": "dataonly", "created": 1783691204906, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Twobuck40", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "There Needs to Be An Age Limit on Serving in Congress", "last_comment_created": 1783705885732, "content": "<p>Maybe an upper limit of 80 or so?</p>\n<p>Simple qualification rule:</p>\n<p>Term for which a person is running must end no later than 180 days after that candidate's 80th birthday.</p>\n<p>Admittedly, Chuck Grassley has remained healthy and lucent well into advance age, but that is not the norm.</p>\n<p>Thurmond, Byrd, Feinstein, McConnell, etc prove there needs to be an age limit.</p>\n<p>How many of you would board a commercial airliner w/ two 80-yr old pilots?</p>\n<p>How many would have surgery performed by an 80-yr old surgeon?</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 11, "score_up": 78, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBqahI9M", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 110, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8721884, "raw_content": "", "author": "ImprerialWalker", "created": 1783684381285, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "ImprerialWalker", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.thedrive.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBqahI9M.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.thedrive.com/news/in-car-cameras-are-now-required-in-europe-us-isnt-far-behind", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "In-Car Cameras Are Now Required in Europe. US Isn\u2019t Far Behind!!!", "last_comment_created": 1783709636555, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 16, "score_up": 110, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "New cars in Europe must have an advanced driver-monitoring system using cameras, sparking privacy concerns.", "large_image": "1sNMxFPaLg3y7loN.png", "title": "In-Car Cameras Are Now Required in Europe. US Isn't Far Behind"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ATBqboa4k", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 31, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8722426, "raw_content": "I woke up one morning, and Obama had taken away my general physician and a healthcare plan I liked.  I just went to work, because that's what people do.\n\nI woke up one morning, and Biden wouldn't let me fly or buy food without proof of getting jabbed. I just went about my business, nearly passing out wearing a face diaper in my local grocery store.\n\nI'm gobsmacked.  Do our neighbors seriously desire more government control over individual freedom? \n\nSheeple.\n\n\n\n", "author": "KuzoKevin", "created": 1783708972609, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Beelzy", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Ask your liberal friends one simple question.  \"How has Trump impacted you, personally?\"", "last_comment_created": 1783713794670, "content": "<p>I woke up one morning, and Obama had taken away my general physician and a healthcare plan I liked.  I just went to work, because that's what people do.</p>\n<p>I woke up one morning, and Biden wouldn't let me fly or buy food without proof of getting jabbed. I just went about my business, nearly passing out wearing a face diaper in my local grocery store.</p>\n<p>I'm gobsmacked.  Do our neighbors seriously desire more government control over individual freedom?</p>\n<p>Sheeple.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 31, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": fals